'''理查德·约翰·哈里森'''（{{lang-en|Richard John Harrison}}，{{bd|1920年|10月8日|1999年|10月17日}}）是一位[[英国|英国]][[解剖学|解剖学]]家，[[剑桥大学|剑桥大学]]教授<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Keverne | first1 = E. B. | doi = 10.1098/rsbm.2005.0012 | title = Sir Richard John Harrison. 8 October 1920 - 17 October 1999: Elected F.R.S. 1973 | journal = [[Biographical_Memoirs_of_Fellows_of_the_Royal_Society|Biographical Memoirs of Fellows of the Royal Society]] | volume = 51 | pages = 185 | year = 2005}}</ref>。他在1961至1967年间担任[[富勒生理学教授|富勒生理学教授]]，1973年当选[[皇家学会|皇家学会]]会士，1977至1979年担任[[大不列颠及爱尔兰解剖学会|大不列颠及爱尔兰解剖学会]]会长<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.anatsoc.org.uk/Portals/0/Documents/AS-officers-hist-final.pdf| title = The Anatomical Society of Great Britain and Ireland - Presidents of the Society| publisher = The Anatomical Society| access-date = 2012-10-21| archive-date = 2018-10-13| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181013222336/http://www.anatsoc.org.uk/Portals/0/Documents/AS-officers-hist-final.pdf| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

